<parameter name="old_string">    helpText: 'Mastering the sales conversation is crucial for converting interested prospects into committed coaching clients and building sustainable revenue for your practice. Prepare a structured consultation format that uncovers client pain points, demonstrates your coaching value, and naturally leads to package enrollment conversations. Practice active listening, ask powerful questions about their desired outcomes, and confidently present your coaching solutions as the bridge between where they are now and where they want to be.'
  }
