<parameter name="new_string">    helpText: 'Mastering the sales conversation is crucial for converting interested prospects into committed coaching clients and building sustainable revenue for your practice. Prepare a structured consultation format that uncovers client pain points, demonstrates your coaching value, and naturally leads to package enrollment conversations. Practice active listening, ask powerful questions about their desired outcomes, and confidently present your coaching solutions as the bridge between where they are now and where they want to be.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-41',
    prompt: 'Create detailed session preparation templates and post-session documentation systems to maintain consistent client progress tracking',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Systematic session preparation and documentation are essential for delivering professional coaching services and demonstrating client progress over time. Develop templates for pre-session client updates, goal review checklists, and post-session summary formats that capture key insights, breakthroughs, and action items from each coaching conversation. This documentation system ensures continuity between sessions and provides valuable progress evidence for both you and your clients.'
  }
];</parameter>
</invoke>
